Supporters of the restoration of a renovated union held a founding congress of their movement in Dushanbe on Saturday. He noted that the majority of the population support Tajik communists' call for the restoration of the Soviet Union. Tajikistan was hit most hard. BFN <F P=106> [Report by ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridnyova] </F> [Text] Dushanbe 16 May TASS -- The Tajik Communist Party has called for the restoration of a renovated Soviet Union in the form of a federation as the only means to ensure the development of the political, economic, and spiritual potential of former Soviet republics. 